<a href="#0" id="0">Notice that syntactic dependencies are both more inclusive and more focused than bag-of-words.</a>
<a href="#1" id="1">They capture relations to words that are far apart and thus “ out-of-reach ” with small window bag-of-words (e.g., the instrument of discover is telescope/prep_with ), and also filter out “ coincidental ” contexts which are within the window but not directly related to the target word (e.g., Australian is not used as the context for discovers.</a>
